# Testing : Test for Smart Reflex RET voltage measurements
# Results : Enable SR for all VDDsMPU IVA and CORE. Suspend the board.Measure the
# VDDs MPU IVA CORE, ensure they have hit RET voltages.Target:OFF mode/Device OFF
